{
  "stem": "20089.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't get the feeling, although it's a long time ago-- but I didn't think I had the feeling as a social worker that these children were missing their parents.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They seemed to be very happy with their madrichim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they varied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had some very young children, nursery school, from about four to five.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there were a lot of schoolchildren, 6 to 12 and 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there were some adolescents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there were the adults who actually were able to come out either with families-- those were very few.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mostly adults who came on their own.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had enormous rooms-- army barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they lived in dormitories, with the-- the madrichim sleeping with them in dormitories-- 20, sometimes 25 to a large dormitory on stretchers with covers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I told you that I graduated as a social worker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did I say that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I did, yes-- and that when I graduated as a social worker, I worked in play centers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my experience in play centers actually was very useful for me in organizing nursery schools, and-- and play centers, and schools.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What were the actual needs of the children, would you say-- the-- the main needs that they had?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that they needed the stimulation of a nursery school environment, and the children who were school-going age had to start learning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The supplies for the schoolchildren came from AJDC.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Munich and Rosenheim were in the American zone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had tremendous, tremendous, tremendous assistance from the American Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were very sympathetic, very helpful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in fact, one of those things that I thought would be very useful for them was to open a gymnasium for the school-going children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I became friendly with some of the GIs.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
